humanMachineDialogue.text: The report indicates that 1 lymph node was examined and it was negative for neoplasm (0/1). This corresponds to New Rule 11: N0 can indicate that all assessed lymph nodes are negative for metastatic carcinoma. Therefore, the N stage is N0.
